- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of a probabilistic model checking tool, which is a software engineering technique. 
- cs.PF (Probability) is a possible category as the paper deals with probabilistic modelling of a storage system. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses the use of a CTMC solver, which involves programming and implementation of the model.
